== 製作 ==

=== 籌備 ===
開展電影拍攝計劃長達將近三年，於2004年10月始雇用同為漫畫書迷[[大衛·班尼歐夫|大衛·班尼歐夫]]（David Benioff）撰寫劇本<ref name=real>{{cite journal|title=David Benioff, Screenwriter of Wolverine: He's One of Us|journal={{link-en|Comics Buyer's Guide|Comics Buyer's Guide}}|author=Mishler, James|date=June 2005|pages=18–20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Michael Fleming|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117911455|title='X' marks spinoff spot|work=Variety |date=2004-10-04|accessdate=2006-09-01}}</ref>。準備編劇期間，一再閱讀{{link-en|巴瑞·史密斯|Barry Windsor-Smith}}（Barry Smith）1991年的「Weapon X」故事，以及[[X戰警|X戰警]]系列作者{{link-en|克里斯·克雷蒙|Chris Claremont}}（Chris Claremont）和[[法蘭克·米勒|法蘭克·米勒]]（Frank Miller）的1982年期限系列裡的角色與他喜愛的故事情節<ref name=real/><ref>{{cite news|author=Daniel Robert Epstein|title=David Benioff|work={{link-en|SuicideGirls|SuicideGirls}}|date=2004-12-28|url=http://suicidegirls.com/interviews/David+Benioff/|accessdate=2008-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207082801/http://suicidegirls.com/interviews/David+Benioff/|archive-date=2008-02-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]演員身為監製參與劇本，想比以往X戰警電影添進更多新的角色<ref>{{cite news|title=Interview – Hugh Jackman|work=CanMag|date=2006-10-15|url=http://www.canmag.com/news/4/3/5413|accessdate=2006-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061030023853/http://www.canmag.com/news/4/3/5413|archive-date=2006-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。編劇大衛想走向「更加著重黑暗面，並且更加殘酷的」故事，以電影分級R級的標準去構思劇本，雖然影片的最後調性仍取決於導演和片商<ref name=real/>，而[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]認為沒有必要將電影製作為R級。

2003年[[新線影業|新線影業]]曾計畫拍攝死侍（Deadpool）獨立於系列的角色電影，由[[萊恩·雷諾斯|萊恩·雷諾斯]]和[[大衛·S·高耶|大衛·S·高耶]]（David S. Goyer）演出，但因當時著重於《[[刀鋒戰士3|刀鋒戰士3]]》（''Blade: Trinity''）宣傳製作，而放棄此拍攝企劃<ref name=deadpooldevelopment>{{cite news|author=Rick Marshall|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/12/11/deadpool-and-gambit-the-long-road-to-x-men-origins-wolverine-and-beyond/|title=Deadpool And Gambit: The Long Road To ‘X-Men Origins: Wolverine’... And Beyond?|work=MTV Movies Blog|date=2008-12-11|accessdate=2008-12-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ql7f76aC?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2593264/deadpool-and-gambit-the-long-road-to-x-men-origins-wolverine-and-beyond/|archive-date=2017-05-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]認為新增角色可增添趣味，而大衛·班尼歐夫也將此角寫入劇本，不過會稍微偏離一些原著設定。同樣，[[金牌手|金牌手]]（Gambit）是本為[[X戰警|X戰警]]系列電影早欲加入的角色，休·傑克曼喜愛金牌手，因為他就像金鋼狼個性般是個「我行我素」的人，角色定位同等於[[X戰警_(電影系列)|X戰警三部曲]]裡金鋼狼和火人（Pyro）微妙關係<ref name=pyro>{{cite news|author=Sam Ashurst|title=Hugh Jackman's First Full Wolverine Interview|work={{link-en|Total Film|Total Film}}|date=2008-12-10|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/hugh-jackman-s-first-full-wolverine-interview|accessdate=2008-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215143124/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/hugh-jackman-s-first-full-wolverine-interview|archive-date=2008-12-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[大衛·艾亞|大衛·艾亞]]（David Ayer）對劇本作出貢獻<ref>{{cite web|url=http://filmbuffonline.com/ReadingRoom/Wolverine.htm|title=''X-Men Origins: Wolverine'' Script Review|publisher=FilmBuffOnLine|accessdate=2009-01-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090120091636/http://filmbuffonline.com/ReadingRoom/Wolverine.htm|archivedate=2009-01-20}}</ref>，大衛·班尼歐夫在2006年10月完成了劇本草稿，因[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]2007年忙於攝製《[[澳大利亞_(電影)|-{澳大利亞}-]]》，而使電影延遲一年進行製作<ref name=ready>{{cite news |author=Karl Schneider |title=Jackman says ''Wolverine'' script is ready |work=Mania Entertainment |date=2006-10-15 |url=http://www.mania.com/jackman-says-wolverine-script-set_article_52545.html |accessdate=2006-10-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080415031030/http://www.mania.com/jackman-says-wolverine-script-set_article_52545.html |archivedate=2008-04-15 }}</ref>。

[[蓋文·胡德|蓋文·胡德]]在2007年7月宣佈選定為本作導演，預定2008年發行<ref>{{cite news|author1=Michael Fleming |author2=Peter Gilstrap |title=Fox says Hood good for ''Wolverine''|work=Variety |date=2007-07-19|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117968868|accessdate=2007-07-20}}</ref>。早先，《[[X戰警_(電影)|X戰警]]》和《[[X戰警2|X戰警2]]》導演[[布萊恩·辛格|布萊恩·辛格]]和《[[X戰警：最後戰役|X戰警：最後戰役]]》導演[[布萊特·瑞納|布萊特·瑞納]]（Brett Ratner）有意回鍋執導系列續集<ref>{{cite news|author=Michael Tsai|title=Sequel to ''Superman Returns'' due in 2009|work={{link-en|The Honolulu Advertiser|The Honolulu Advertiser}}|date=2006-11-08|url=http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2006/Nov/08/br/br0948627351.html|accessdate=2007-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012002444/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2006/Nov/08/br/br0948627351.html|archive-date=2007-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="multiple">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1526112/story.jhtml|title=Juggernaut Weighs In On 'X-Men' Spinoffs|last=Carroll|first=Larry|publisher=MTV|date=2006-03-14|accessdate=2009-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060508033203/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1526112/story.jhtml|archive-date=2006-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他導演[[亞歷山大·阿加|亞歷山大·阿加]]（Alexandre Aja）和[[連恩·懷斯曼|連恩·懷斯曼]]也充滿興趣<ref>{{cite news|author=Sean Elliott|title=''The Hills Have Eyes'' Director Alexandre Aja gets grisly|work=iF Magazine|date=2006-03-11|url=http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=1444|accessdate=2007-11-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071130193111/http://ifmagazine.com/feature.asp?article=1444|archivedate=2007-11-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Edward Douglas|title=Len Wiseman on ''Wolverine''|work=Mania Entertainment|date=2007-07-22|url=http://www.mania.com/len-wiseman-wolverine_article_107546.html|accessdate=2007-07-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007180753/http://www.mania.com/len-wiseman-wolverine_article_107546.html|archivedate=2012-10-07}}</ref>，曾爭取拍攝的[[查克·史奈德|查克·史奈德]]（Zack Snyder）最後也放下這部影片，轉而執導《[[守護者_(電影)|守護者]]》<ref>{{cite news|author=Robert Sanchez|title=Exclusive Interview: Zack Snyder Is Kickin' Ass With ''300'' and ''Watchmen''!|work=IESB|date=2007-02-13|url=http://iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1883&Itemid=99|accessdate=2008-02-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070217033245/http://iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1883&Itemid=99|archivedate=2007-02-17}}</ref>。[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]在電影《[[黑幫暴徒|黑幫暴徒]]》（''Tsotsi''）中看見類似羅根和要角之間的關係<ref name=empire>{{cite news|author=O'Hara, Helen|title=Weapon X|work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]]|date=January 2009|pages=85–90}}</ref>，非漫畫書迷的導演葛文·胡德解釋，他「意識到金鋼狼角色，事實上我認為他吸引人之處，在一些方面是那巨大謊言的人生，充滿很多他所厭惡或喜歡的人，並經常與他自己內心的純淨戰爭」<ref name=whywolvie>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615015932/http://www.ugo.com/ugo/html/article/?id=17949|archivedate=2011-06-15|title=Rendition Interviews|author1=Kyle Braun|author2=Jordan Riefe|lastauthoramp=yes|work={{link-en|UGO Networks|UGO Networks|UGO}}|date=2007-09-29|url=http://www.ugo.com/ugo/html/article/?id=17949|accessdate=2007-09-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。導演認為電影主旨集中於金鋼狼的內在衝突，著重在他的野性和人性之間掙扎。葛文·胡德喜愛前幾部電影，但下決心將本片打造一種不同的感受<ref name=violence>{{cite news|author=Larry Carroll|title=''Wolverine'' Director, Hugh Jackman Digging Their Claws Into ''X-Men'' Spinoff|publisher=MTV|date=2007-10-03|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1571060/20070301/story.jhtml|accessdate=2007-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011023115/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1571060/20070301/story.jhtml|archive-date=2007-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]10月宣佈2009年5月1日發行首映X戰警前傳<ref name=may>{{cite news|author=McClintock, Pamela|title=''Wolverine'' Claws on May '09 Date – Liev Schreiber in Final Talks for 'X-Men' Role|work=Variety |date=2007-10-17|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117974247|accessdate=2010-01-17}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
2007年末，初期在[[悉尼|雪梨]]的{{link-en|福斯澳洲片廠|Fox Studios Australia}}拍攝<ref>{{cite news|author={{link-en|Staff writer|Staff writer}}|title=X-Men Cameras Set To Roll Down South|work={{link-en|The Dominion Post (Wellington)|The Dominion Post (Wellington)|The Dominion Post}}|date=2008-01-22|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/229636|accessdate=2010-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090707221732/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/229636|archive-date=2009-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2008年1月18日在[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]進行主要攝影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10488429|title=Queenstown gets ready for X-Men|work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]]|first=Jarrod|last=Booker|date=2008-01-24|accessdate=2012-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121120185539/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10488429|archive-date=2012-11-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，場景地點包括[[但尼丁|但尼丁]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Shooting for ''Wolverine'' Set to Commence in South Island|work={{link-en|TV3 (New Zealand)|TV3 (New Zealand)|TV3}}|date=2008-01-27|url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Shooting-for-Wolverine-set-to-commence-in-South-Island/tabid/209/articleID/44401/Default.aspx|accessdate=2008-11-27|archive-date=2013-02-23|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130223003742/http://www.3news.co.nz/Shooting-for-Wolverine-set-to-commence-in-South-Island/tabid/209/articleID/44401/Default.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。位於[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]][[南島|南島]][[奧塔哥地區|奧塔哥地區]]的[[皇后鎮|皇后鎮]]當地勞工反對福斯在溜冰場囤積拍片用炸藥，於是下令搬移至另一區域<ref name=xplosive>{{cite news|author=Button, Katie|title=''X-Men'' Film Upsets Local Council|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date=2008-01-24|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a87256/x-men-film-upsets-local-council.html|accessdate=2010-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611013621/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a87256/x-men-film-upsets-local-council.html|archive-date=2011-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這些炸藥用來拍攝農場遭到飛彈發射爆破一幕，同時使用四架攝影機多角度同步拍攝<ref>{{cite news|author=Williams, David|title=Explosive End for SI Blockbuster|work={{link-en|The Press|The Press}}|date=2007-11-03|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/11223|accessdate=2010-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505185330/http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/11223|archive-date=2009-05-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]與環保專家開會，拍攝過程盡量不破壞環境，達成協議才允許拍攝<ref>{{cite news|author=Morris, Chris|title=Film Crew Commits to Green Ethic|work={{link-en|Otago Daily Times|Otago Daily Times}}|date=2008-01-29}}</ref>。

拍攝持續在福斯片廠和[[美國|美國]][[路易西安納州|路易西安納州]][[紐奧良|紐奧良]]進行<ref name=may>{{cite news|author=McClintock, Pamela|title=''Wolverine'' Claws on May '09 Date – Liev Schreiber in Final Talks for 'X-Men' Role|work=Variety |date=2007-10-17|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117974247|accessdate=2010-01-17}}</ref>。[[悉尼|雪梨]]著名的{{link-en|風頭鸚鵡島|Cockatoo Island (Western Australia)}}（Cockatoo Island）作為史崔克上將的實驗工廠，那裡大量現成建築節省在製作特效方面的資金<ref name=empire/>。電影製作預測將帶起雪梨六千萬美元的經濟<ref>{{cite news|author={{link-en|Staff writer|Staff writer}}|title=Jackman's 'Wolverine' Starts Shooting in Sydney – Australian Actor Hugh Jackman Will Start Filming His New Movie, ''X-Men Origins: Wolverine'', in Sydney Today|work={{link-en|ABC News (Australia)|ABC News (Australia)|ABC News}}|date=2008-02-25|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2008-02-25/jackmans-wolverine-starts-shooting-in-sydney/1053110|accessdate=2010-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110233842/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2008-02-25/jackmans-wolverine-starts-shooting-in-sydney/1053110|archive-date=2012-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主要拍攝在5月23日前告一段落，第二單位在紐西蘭繼續攝製直到3月23日，預定跟隨第一單位持續攝製二個星期<ref>{{cite news|author=Bentley, David|title=Filming wraps on Wolverine as Jackman offers chance to meet him for lunch|work={{link-en|Coventry Telegraph|Coventry Telegraph}}|date=2008-05-29|url=http://blogs.coventrytelegraph.net/thegeekfiles/2008/05/post.html|accessdate=2012-06-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120629050118/http://blogs.coventrytelegraph.net/thegeekfiles/2008/05/post.html|archivedate=2012-06-29}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
=== 特別事件 ===
2009年4月初，網上驚現由內部泄漏出的《X戰警：金鋼狼》未完成完整版，除了故事相對比較完整外，但在特效方面可以看到仍然有未抹去的鋼絲以及一些未完成的特效<ref name="bbcleak">{{cite news|title=New Wolverine film leaked online|work=BBC News|date=2009-04-01|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7977265.stm|accessdate=2009-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090402012139/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7977265.stm|archive-date=2009-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reutersleak">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/filmNews/idUSTRE53113T20090402|title=X-Men pic "Wolverine" leaks online|agency=Reuters|date=2009-04-02|accessdate=2009-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090403211058/http://www.reuters.com/article/filmNews/idUSTRE53113T20090402|archive-date=2009-04-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="apleak">{{cite news|url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/leak-doesn-t-keep-fans-away-from-wolverine-1.1230378|title=Leak doesn't keep fans away from 'Wolverine'|agency=Associated Press|date=2009-05-04|accessdate=2009-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104205420/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/movies/leak-doesn-t-keep-fans-away-from-wolverine-1.1230378|archive-date=2016-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。起初不少網友認為是愚人節禮物，但經證實消息電影皆為實在，並有高達十萬人以上下載，由於事件嚴重，[[美國|美國]]方面出動了[[联邦调查局|FBI]]調查事件<ref name="reutersleak" />。有認為是電影特效的製作公司洩漏出去。電影公司曾經為此擔心票房受到影響，但結果顯示事件並無影響到票房，甚至可能讓人更多的關注該影片。

未完成版及原版長度皆為107分鐘，但導演[[蓋文·胡德|蓋文·胡德]]表示，正版暗藏兩段神祕結尾，而未完成版則沒有<ref name="apleak" />。

=== 評價 ===
電影收穫了影評人的普遍差評。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的253篇專業影評文章，其中95篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為38%，平均得分5.1分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wolverine/|title=X-Men Origins: Wolverine reviews|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2011-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426021435/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wolverine|archive-date=2016-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的40篇評論文章，其中9篇予以好評，11篇差評，19篇褒貶不一，平均分為39（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.metacritic.com/movie/x-men-origins-wolverine|title= X-Men Origins: Wolverine Reviews|publisher= CBS|work= Metacritic|accessdate= 2013-05-03|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/699xV2D8J?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/x-men-origins-wolverine|archive-date= 2012-07-14|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《X戰警：金鋼狼》於2009年4月29日於英國、丹麥、南非和澳大利亞發布；美國及加拿大則於5月1日上映。片商有在其官網舉行比賽，以決定4月27日全球首映的位置。最終，在[[亞利桑那|亞利桑那]]坦佩市市場的哈金斯贏得比賽<ref>{{cite news|first=Bill|last=Goodykoontz|title=Tempe wins Wolverinep remiere|url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/2009/04/19/20090419wolverine0420.html|publisher={{link-en|The Arizona Republic|The Arizona Republic}}|date=2009-04-19|accessdate=2009-05-01}}</ref>。但由於該國[[2009年H1N1流感大流行墨西哥情況|H1N1流感]]的爆發，墨西哥的發布被推遲到5月底<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/977/977717p1.html|title=Hasta Luego, Wolverine|last=Jim|first=Vejvoda|date=2009-04-29|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2009-04-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505182837/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/977/977717p1.html|archivedate=2009-05-05}}</ref>。

雖然來自影評人的評論褒貶不一，但本片仍不失為一個票房上的成功。根據[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]統計，《X戰警：金鋼狼》在美國及加拿大的票房約為179,883,157美元，其他地區收穫193,179,707美元，全球總計373,062,864美元<ref name="mojo"/>。

